Author: angerexic
Text: Yeah, the pressure is intense. Even more so with this friend because she’s a few years younger than me (she’s 16) and I’d die if I passed any of my food anxieties onto her. And I’ll try, Thanks for the reassurance.

Author: rqrqsj
Text: Wow I totally feel you. That pressure of having someone over and having to eat every meal is a nightmare scenario. You’ll be okay! Try to relax and focus on your friend (lol I know it’s impossible).
